            "title": "港股開升13點   恒瑞首掛飆逾29%  生科股揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數競價時段開報23557點，升13點或0.06%，恒生科技指數升3點或0.07%，報5255點，恒生國企指數升8點或0.1%，報8566點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交37.18億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"恒瑞醫藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/600276-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"恒瑞醫藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/600276-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">恒瑞醫藥官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒瑞醫藥(01276)首掛，較招股價升29.4%，報57元，成交居首。同樣首掛的生科股MIRXES升24.46%，報29元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">信達生物(01810)升5.42%報59.3元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">嗶哩嗶哩(09626)額外發9000萬美元票據，開升2.14%，報143.3元。網易水09999)升1.93%，報190.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧德時代(03750)升2.18%，報337元。</p>\n</div>",
