            "title": "中國宏橋發行2.7億美元優先無抵押票據",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國宏橋(01378)宣佈，昨天交易時段後訂立協議，發行本金總額2.7億美元2028年到期優先票據，息率6.925厘。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國宏橋官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230808_FI_source-web_中國宏橋2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國宏橋官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230808_FI_source-web_中國宏橋2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國宏橋官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公布稱，新加坡交易所已原則上批准票據在新加坡交易所上市及掛牌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">票據發行的估計所得款項總額將為2.7億美元。本公司擬將是次發售的所得款項淨額用作一般公司用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14951542-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%ae%8f%e6%a9%8b%e7%99%bc%e8%a1%8c2-7%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e5%84%aa%e5%85%88%e7%84%a1%e6%8a%b5%e6%8a%bc%e7%a5%a8%e6%93%9a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230808_FI_source-web_1378_fb.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-23 09:00:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
